title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs Newcastle United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Newcastle are winless in all seven of their away Premier League games against Brighton, the joint-most they have visited an opponent in the competition without ever winning. It’s the outright most Brighton have faced a side without losing at home in the Premier League. Following their 1-0 win in October, Brighton could complete their third league double over Newcastle, after 1978-79 and 2020-21.

title: AFC Bournemouth vs Aston Villa - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Bournemouth lost 1-0 at home to Aston Villa in their first ever Premier League match in August 2015. Since then, the Cherries are unbeaten in three at home to the Villans, scoring exactly two goals in each. Aston Villa are unbeaten in their last four Premier League games against Bournemouth, having lost four in a row against the Cherries before this.

title: EPL Stories 2024/2025
description: Showcases the personalities who have shaped the Premier League era with a focus on the stories that resonate with international audiences.

title: Manchester United vs West Ham United - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Manchester United are unbeaten in their last 16 Premier League home games against West Ham, winning each of their last four without conceding. West Ham have won three of their last four Premier League games against Man Utd, as many as in their previous 28 beforehand. They’re looking to complete their first league double over the Red Devils since 2006-07.

title: Liverpool vs Arsenal - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Liverpool are unbeaten in their last 14 home games against Arsenal in all competitions since a 2-0 loss in the Premier League in September 2012. Arsenal are unbeaten in their last five Premier League games against Liverpool, their longest run without defeat against the Reds since a run of eight between October 2007 and April 2011.

title: FA CUP Review SF 2024/2025
description: All the very best action from the latest round of the English FA Cup

title: Southampton vs Manchester City - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Southampton have won just one of their last 15 Premier League games against Man City, a 1-0 home win in July 2020. Man City won the reverse fixture 1-0 against Southampton, but haven’t kept a clean sheet in consecutive league meetings with the Saints since doing so in both meetings of the 2014-15 campaign.

title: Nottingham Forest vs Leicester City - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37
description: Nottingham Forest are looking to complete their first league double over Leicester since 1994-95, following their 3-1 win at the King Power Stadium in October. Leicester have won just one of their last 18 away league games against Nottingham Forest, a 3-2 win in May 2013.

title: Wolverhampton Wanderers vs Brighton and Hove Albion - English Premier League 2024/25 Week 37

title: Real Betis vs Osasuna - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Real Betis have won nine of their last 10 LaLiga matches against Osasuna, scoring in all 10, their longest run of scoring against the Reds in the competitions history. Osasuna have lost their last six away matches against Real Betis in LaLiga, their worst consecutive losing streak against the Betis side in their history in the top-flight.

title: La Liga World 2024/25 Ep.38
description: A program of interviews and reports I which all LALIGA clubs are represented The program lasts 26 minutes and every week presents all the latest personal stories and the more human-interest side of the competition in a slow-paced and polished format.

title: Leganes vs Espanyol - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Leganes have not lost any of their last three LaLiga matches against Espanyol, their longest unbeaten run against the Perico team in the top-flight. Espanyol have not won any of their last three away matches against CD Leganes in all competitions, failing to score in all three. This is their worst all-time run without a win or a goal away from home against the Pepineros.

title: Athletic Bilbao vs Deportivo Alaves - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Athletic Club have not lost any of their last six LaLiga matches against Alaves, their second-longest unbeaten run against the Vitoria side in the competition, following their first 14 top-flight clashes. Deportivo Alaves have picked up points in four of their last eight away matches against Athletic Club in LaLiga, having lost each of their first 10 visits to the club in the competition.

title: Valencia vs Getafe - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Valencia have won only four of their last 17 LaLiga matches against Getafe, after winning 12 of their previous 16 top-flight matches. Getafe have lost each of their last three LaLiga away matches against Valencia, after picking up points in their previous five visits to Mestalla in the competition.

title: Barcelona vs Real Madrid - LaLiga 2024/25
description: Barcelona have won their last three matches against Real Madrid in all competitions, only once in the entire history of ElClásico, between 2008 and 2010 under Josep Guardiola, have the Blaugrana managed 4+ consecutive wins. Real Madrid have won four of their last five away matches against FC Barcelona in all competitions, achieving the same number of victories as in their previous 19 visits to Barcelona.

title: LaLiga BEST 11 - Luis García
description: Luis Garcia was a striker who played 8 seasons in La Liga. He played for Barcelona, Real Valladolid, Atletico Madrid and Real Racing in La Liga. In his career he played 473 games, scoring 115 goals.

title: Celta de Vigo vs Sevilla - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Celta de Vigo have picked up points in five of their last six LaLiga matches against Sevilla, after losing seven of their previous 11 in the competition. Sevilla have not lost any of their last four away matches against Celta de Vigo in LaLiga, their longest unbeaten run away from home against the Galician side in their top-flight history.

title: Real Betis vs Osasuna - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 35
description: Real Betis have won nine of their last 10 LaLiga matches against Osasuna, scoring in all 10, their longest run of scoring against the Reds in the competitions history. Osasuna have lost their last six away matches against Real Betis in LaLiga, their worst consecutive losing streak against the Betis side in their history in the top-flight.

title: LaLiga Talking Football 2024/2025 Ep.5
description: TALKING FOOTBALL is an exclusive unique window into Spanish football and the people that have made it what it is. We dress as coaches and join their meetings and private discussions. description: Monaco and Lyon will meet for the 117th time in Ligue 1, the opponents the two teams have faced the most in the division. Monaco have won 48 of these encounters, winning more only against Rennes and Strasbourg, but have lost 44 times to OL, the opponent who has beaten them the most. Monaco have lost just one of their last nine Ligue 1 games, having lost four of their previous eight.

title: Rennes vs Nice - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Rennes have won only three of their 19 meetings against Nice over the last 10 seasons in Ligue 1 but have won the last two at home. Rennes have lost 18 of their 32 Ligue 1 2024-25 matches, their highest total at this stage of the season since 1986-87. That is also the last season during which SRFC conceded more than 18 defeats in total.

title: Ligue 1 Highlights 2024/25 Week 32
description: Each Ligue 1 Match week is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

title: Angers SCO vs Strasbourg - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Angers have lost each of their last three home games against Strasbourg in Ligue 1, having lost just four of the first 22 league meetings. Only against Paris SG and Monaco are the SCO on a longer losing streak at home in the competition. Angers have won two of their last four Ligue 1 games, having won just one of their previous 10 in the division.

title: Montpellier vs PSG - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Paris SG have won each of their last 11 games against Montpellier in Ligue 1, totaling 33 wins against MHSC in the top-flight. Only Monaco have beaten Montpellier more often in the competition. Montpellier have conceded 41 goals in their last 10 Ligue 1 games against Paris SG, the highest tally of goals conceded by a team in 10 consecutive matches against the same opponent in the history of L1.

title: Stadium of Fears
description: Everyone knows the biggest stadiums in the world. But sometimes its the smallest stadiums that are the most intimidating for players, due to their fans and their fervor. Several big names in football tell you about their experiences in these stadiums where it can sometimes be difficult to play.

title: Toulouse vs Lens - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Toulouse have lost their last three home games against Lens in Ligue 1 without scoring a single goal and could achieve their longest run of this type against the same opponent in the competition. Toulouse have won only one of their last eight matches in Ligue 1, but it was the most recent against Rennes.

title: Auxerre vs Nantes - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 33
description: Auxerre has won each of their last six Ligue 1 home games against Nantes, their longest current run against an opponent currently in the division. Auxerre have lost three of their last four Ligue 1 games, as many as in their previous 12.

title: Werder Bremen vs RB Leipzig - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: RB Leipzig are unbeaten in their last 10 competitive games against SV Werder Bremen, winning eight of them. Of teams currently in the top flight that they have faced more than four times, Leipzig’s points-per-game average against SVW isn’t higher against any other side. SV Werder Bremen sit in eighth place with 47 points – they last had more points after 32 Bundesliga games in 2009/10 when they last qualified for Europe. SVW are three points behind sixth-placed RB Leipzig – since the introduction of three points per win, only Karlsruher SC in 1996/97 and Hamburger SV in 1995/96 have ever made up as large a gap to sixth over the last two matchdays.

title: Bochum vs Mainz 05 - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: VfL Bochum average just 0.38 points per Bundesliga game against 1. FSV Mainz 05, their lowest return against any team. Bochum have won just one of their 13 top-flight meetings, collecting only one point from their six Bundesliga clashes since that victory. Only VfL Wolfsburg are currently on a longer wait for a Bundesliga win than VfL Bochum and 1. FSV Mainz 05. This is Mainz’s longest spell without victory since between November 2023 and February 2024.

title: Bundesliga - Special 2024/2025 - Roots: Kane, Schick and Ekitike
description: Three strikers, three stories, one common goal: scoring goals for the teams success. But what shaped Harry Kane, Patrik Schick, and Hugo Ekitike on their paths to the top? In the 26-minute documentary Roots – Kane, Schick and Ekitike, we travel back to the beginnings of these Bundesliga stars. For FC Bayern Munchen player Harry Kane, we trace his roots in Chingford, a suburban town in East London. We also speak with youth coaches from his first club, Ridgeway Rovers, as well as former Tottenham player and England international Jermain Defoe. title: Bayer Leverkusen vs Borussia Dortmund - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: After winning the reverse fixture, Bayer 04 Leverkusen could now do a league double over Borussia Dortmund for the first time since 2006/07. However, their three-game wait at home for a victory against BVB in the Bundesliga is currently their longest against any top-flight side. Bayer 04 Leverkusen are unbeaten in their last seven Bundesliga games – only Union Berlin are currently enjoying a longer undefeated spell. However, B04’s 2-2 draw in Freiburg was their third draw in their last four games and their 11th overall in 2024/25, a joint league high together with RB Leipzig. Since 2000, the Werkself have only ever shared the points more often in a season in 2009/10.

title: Stuttgart vs Augsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: VfB Stuttgart are unbeaten in their last seven competitive games against FC Augsburg, winning each of the last four without conceding a single goal. title: Eintracht Frankfurt vs St. Pauli - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 33
description: Eintracht Frankfurt, founded in 1899, are now set to play their 1,899th Bundesliga game. They are still unbeaten in their six home matches against St. Pauli and have only hosted RB Leipzig more often in the top flight without ever losing. Eintracht Frankfurt are unbeaten in their last 14 Bundesliga games against promoted sides, winning each of the last four. title: Al Ahli (KSA) vs Kawasaki (JPN) - AFC Champions League Elite 2024/25 - Final
description: Al-Ahli will face Kawasaki Frontale for the first time in the AFC Champions League elite and for the first time against a Japanese team. Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament. title: The Outdoor Sports Show 2025
description: Welcome to this episode of Outdoor Sports Show, the TV magazine programme which takes you to the best events and introduces you to the characters from the action-packed world of outdoor sports. We strongly believe that from the many different paths we take in life, some of them must be dirt paths, because filling our lives with adventure gives us some great stories to share and this is what the outdoor sports show will bring to you!We now travel to the United Arab Emirates for another marathon. Staged under the auspices of the Dubai Sports Council, the Dubai Marathon celebrated its 24th anniversary with thousands of runners taking to the area around the iconic Burj Al Arab. We stay in the U

title: World Sailing Show 2025
description: The World Sailing Show 2025 brings you the most thrilling moments from elite sailing competitions around the globe. From high-speed foiling action to tactical offshore battles, this episode covers top events like the America’s Cup, SailGP, and The Ocean Race. Meet the world’s best sailors, explore cutting-edge boat technology, and witness the drama of high-stakes racing on the water.

title: Food Tech: Chinese Take Out
description: Since an influx of Chinese immigrants to America in the mid 1800s, Americans have devoured Chinese take-out. But have you ever wondered whats really in an egg roll?

title: UFO Hunters: Underwater Alien Bases
description: From 1987 to the early 1990s, Florida was inundated with UFO sightings, while 90 miles away at Guantanamo Bay, USOs (Unidentified Submerged Objects) were seen rising out of the ocean.

title: How The Earth Was Made: Asteroids
description: Most major geological processes require millions of year to become noticeable. Meteor impacts are exceptions which can cause comparable changes in seconds.

title: Engineering An Empire: The Aztecs
description: In less than 200 years, the Aztecs went from a tribe of nomads into the most powerful civilisation the New World had ever known. How did they achieve such greatness?

title: In Search Of Aliens: The Mystery Of Cyclops
description: The mysterious Mediterranean island of Malta lies south of Sicily and is home to megalithic structures built by a mysterious prehistoric society. Who were the people that built these sophisticated structures?

title: Rome: Rise And Fall Of An Empire: The Barbarian General
description: Emperor Theodosius enlisted Goth mercenaries to fight for the Empire, but how did he ensure loyalty? By giving command to the half-Vandal, half-Roman general, Stilicho.

title: Hunting Hitler: The Tunnel
description: In 2014, the FBI discovered the possibility that Hitler may have escaped to South America. With declassified intelligence providing new clues, Hunting Hitler attempts to solve the mystery surrounding the demise of the biggest criminal of all time.

title: Where Did It Come From?: Ancient China: Agriculture
description: Host Michael Guillen travels to China to explore the roots of modern agricultural genius. He studies how the ancient Chinese invented advanced farming technology long before the west would use anything like it.

description: From the icy docks of Bristol to the tropical paradise of the Caribbean, follow the incredible journey of fearsome buccaneers and their hunt for treasure and booty.

description: MonsterQuest looks into claims that large cats are on the prowl in the forests of the United States.

title: Digging For The Truth: Quest For King Solomons Gold
description: Host Josh Bernstein searches for the long-lost land of Ophir, home of King Solomons vast treasures. But can he succeed where so many before him have failed?

title: The Universe: Colonising Space
description: Examine the efforts under way to establish a human colony on Mars, including plans to grow food, recycle waste water and introduce a breathable atmosphere.

title: Ancient Aliens: Beyond Roswell
description: Explores the controversial theory that extraterrestrials have visited Earth. From the age of the dinosaurs to ancient Egypt.

title: UFO Files: Deep Sea Ufos: Red Alert
description: In this hour, well dive deeper into the ongoing mystery of USOs, Underwater Submerged Objects, UFOs that have reportedly been witnessed going into and out of Earths oceans.

title: Unidentified: Inside Americas UFO Investigation: The Atomic Connection
description: An encounter in the American heartland indicates a disturbing twist to the UFO phenomenon. The team follows a trail of explosive evidence connecting UFOs to the most destructive weapons in human history.

title: Looting History: Risky Business: Michael Steinhardt...
description: ...and the Greek Pot of Gold: Michael Steinhardt, the largest private collector of antiquities, is forced to turn over $70 million dollars� worth of stolen loot and banned from collecting. His undoing comes after a four-year investigation known as Operation Demetra.

title: Looting History: Making A Killing: Douglas Latchford...
description: ...and the Cambodian Killing Fields: As Douglas Latchford is accused of masterminding a multimillion-dollar racket in loot stolen from Cambodias killing fields, museums and collectors face the grim reality that theyre in possession of stolen property.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: On Their Marks
description: Rick, Marty, and the team return to Oak Island and immediately uncover evidence of a mysterious tunnel in the Money Pit.

title: American Pickers: The Diy Delorean
description: Mike meets someone who shares his passion for vintage treasures, this leads him to a space filled with items that seem to be untouched by time.

title: Pawn Stars: Off the Rails
description: Chum gets his hands on a trio of vintage comic strip characters; will the seller play with his emotions, and toy around with a deal? Next, a book by Amelia Earhart flies into the shop. Will Rick dare to make a deal, or will the price soar too high?

title: Prison Chronicles: Dannemora
description: Dannemora, located in the frigid Adirondack mountains, its nickname is "little Siberia." Officially called the Clinton Correctional facility, this foreboding prison is commonly known as Dannemora, named after the town where it is built.

title: Prison Chronicles: San Quentin
description: San Quentin located in Marin County on the San Francisco Bay is Californias oldest prison dating back to the gold rush, and home to the states only gas chamber. Here three men have tried to find their way out of the prisons clutches.

title: The UnXplained With William Shatner: Secrets of Ancient Structures
description: Scattered across the globe lie mysterious ruins. These age-old structures stand as silent sentinels from the past, their true history seemingly erased by time. Can modern archaeology unravel the enigma of how - and why - these wonders were built?

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators Of The Forge: A Champions Quest
description: Our defending champion currently has four wins under his belt but will face his toughest challenge yet in forging the very weapon used to assassinate Julius Caesar, the Pugio Dagger.

description: River Hunters sees Rick and river expert Beau searching the unexplored rivers and waterways of Britain, unearthing treasures from the past which reveal how ancestors used to live.

title: River Hunters: The Battle of Killiecrankie
description: The team find evidence from one of Scotlands bloodiest eras as they wade through the waters of the River Garry in the Scottish Highlands, the site of the first major clash between Highland Jacobites and the government army.

title: River Hunters: Viking Invasion
description: Rick and Beau tackle the mighty River Ouse in Yorkshire, hunting for evidence of Britain’s most notorious sea-faring raiders - the Vikings. With a find potentially dating to the 11th Century battle, it’s a river hunt of epic proportions.

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: Suez
description: Fresh from diving on the Mary Rose and still on the hunt for underwater artefacts that tell the story of the British Empire, Ross hops round the coast from Portsmouth to Plymouth, then on to the Gulf of Suez.

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: Nazi Menace
description: In this episode Ross continues his diving quest in the crystal clear waters of the Red Sea off the coast of Egypt. It’s a deeply personal journey as Ross’ grandfather fought in the North Africa campaign during World War Two.

title: Ross Kemp: Deep Sea Treasure Hunter: D-Day
description: Ross goes on the hunt for wrecks that tell the story of D-Day, the 1944 Allied invasion of Occupied France, and discovers how winning wasn’t just a case of superior firepower and numbers, but also ingenuity.

title: Ross Kemp: Shipwreck Treasure Hunter: The U-Boat Terror
description: Ross completes his specialist SCUBA training under the expert tutelage of dive Supervisor Neil Brock, and inspired by the stories of his shipwrecked relatives, he heads up to the Royal Navy’s historic naval base in the far northerly Orkney Islands.

title: Mystery Places: Episode 12
description: Explore the most dangerous hotel in the world, visit the housing development in Luoyang, China - a copy of an Austrian UNESCO village - and check out the most fascinating beaches in the world.

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: Across The Pond
description: While on a research mission in England, Marty, Alex, and Charles are thrilled to uncover more evidence connecting the Knights Templar to the Oak Island mystery.

title: American Pickers: Carnival Crash Out
description: In Minnesota, Mike and Jersey go hog wild for a four-generation carny collection complete with carousel horses, toy tanks, and bumper cars. Down the road in New Hampshire, on a special mission for Robbie, the guys head to Rogers analogue laboratory.

title: Pawn Stars: Wanted: Pawned or Alive
description: Rick is ready for some football when a Super Bowl bucket hat rushes into the shop. Can he score big, or will he fumble the deal? Corey and Chum are envious when Spencer brings in an Incredible Hulk comic book. Will their strongest offer be enough?

title: The Curse Of Oak Island: The Chosen
description: Rick, Marty, and the Oak Island team go in-depth with Matty Blake on locations where they hope to unearth buried treasure in the Money Pit area.

title: Beyond Skinwalker Ranch: Tumbleweeds And Uaps
description: Andy and Paul investigate a desert hotbed of strange activity where local lore speaks of an entity called "Goldie", they find that not only is there scientific evidence backing up these stories, but other entities may not want these stories told.

title: Forged In Fire: Gladiators Of The Forge: The Final Battles
description: Its back to the Colosseum for the last two one-on-one battles. The reigning champion has defeated six opponents, but now must face a returning challenger and forge the intricate acinaces sword.

description: Fortune hunter Allan Quatermain teams up with a resourceful woman to help her find her missing father lost in the wilds of 1900s Africa.
